title: Peter Asher - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/9/22
itunes:title: Peter Asher - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/9/22
description:
Guest host Ian Punnett and musician Peter Asher of the 1960s duo Peter & Gordon discuss his career as a singer, his Grammy award winning work as a producer with artists like James Taylor and Linda Ronstadt, and how he inspired the movie character Austin Powers.
